			JustDoIt
----------------------------------
----------------------------------

**Achieved:
1. Create a TODO list app with the following fields ­ To do item ­TextArea
­ 	To be completed by ­ Date
­ 	Status (Completed|Pending) ­ switch
­ 	Image (Optional) ­ Imageview
2. iOS and Android must be supported. (If you don't have a Mac to support iOS let us know as soon as you receive the test)
3. As a user I should be able to create a new TODO. All created tasks are marked as pending.
4. As a user I should be able to see all my TODOs in a list.

**Partially Achieved
5. As a user I should be able to toggle between completed or pending TODOs ­ Brownie point
8. As a user I should be able to complete a task and you should differentiate between completed and pending tasks using appropriate UI changes.
11. As a user I should be able to add an image to each task, either from the gallery or directly from the camera. ­ Brownie point


**Pending
6. As a user I should be able to edit a TODO.
9. As a user I should be able to share a TODO task. At least email and SMS is required, FB and TW are a bonus. ­ Brownie point
10. As a user I should be able to close the app and open it again without losing any TODO tasks. ­ Brownie point
12. As a user If i click on the thumbnail image, I should be able to see this in full screen in a separate window.­ Brownie point